<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <h2>New Sign-In Alert</h2>
  <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
  <p>We noticed a new sign-in to your account from a new device or location:</p>
  <ul style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px;">
    <li><strong>Device:</strong> {{device}}</li>
    <li><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</li>
    <li><strong>Date & Time:</strong> {{dateTime}}</li>
  </ul>
  <p>If this was you, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
  <p>If this was <strong>not</strong> you, your account may be at risk. Please change your password immediately by clicking the button below:</p>
  <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #e53935; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
    Reset Password
  </a>
  <p>This link will expire in {{expiryHours}} hour(s).</p>
  <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
</div>
